nib.text:
This lost dog, Koffee, is back home after having been missing for five days. Volunteers across Minneapolis helped to bring him home using the [Shadow](https://app.adjust.com/m5ap19b) app.

His owner wanted to share this message: "5 days later Koffee was found today right near where he was lost by the highway. He was found scared, and was so excited when reunited with me. He is unharmed."
